annotationA: Probable U2 small nuclear ribonucleoprotein A; U2A is a protein component of the U2 snRNP. The U2 snRNP combines with other snRNPs on the pre-mRNA to assemble a spliceosome
annotationB: Splicing factor U2AF 50 kDa subunit; Necessary for the splicing of pre-mRNA. Binds to the polypyrimidine tract of introns early during spliceosome assembly (By similarity)
